      <div xml:id="szovsr-r06503"><!-- t10l7prae -->
        <head xml:id="szovsr-r06503-Hd1e101">Praeambulum</head>
        <p xml:id="szovsr-r06503-d1e103">
          <cb ed="#V" n="d"/>
          <lb ed="#C" n="15"/>LIBER SEPTIMUS
          <lb ed="#C" n="16"/>DE
          <lb ed="#C" n="17"/>PROFBESSIS TRIUM VOTORUM
          <lb ed="#C" n="18"/>ET COADJUTORIBUS FORMATIS SOCINIATIS.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="szovsr-r06503-d1e116">
          <cb ed="#V" n="e"/>
          <lb ed="#C" n="19"/>Introductio ad sequentem librum septumum.
          <lb ed="#C" n="20"/>— Constat ex Bullis et Constitutionibus 
          Socie<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="21"/>tatis, quas infra, c. 1, referemus, praeter 
          pro<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="22"/>fessos quatuor votorum, esse alios presbyteros
          <lb ed="#C" n="23"/>religiosos, qui ad ipsos professos in 
          spirituali<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="24"/>bus ministeriis juvandos in Societate 
          reci<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="25"/>piuntur , eique alio genere professionis vel
          <lb ed="#C" n="26"/>unionis incorporantur, et in ultimo quodam
          <lb ed="#C" n="27"/>gradu religioso constituuntur, quos professos
          <lb ed="#C" n="28"/>trium votorum, aut coadjutores spirituales 
          for<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="29"/>matos appellamus. De his ergo nunc 
          commo<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="30"/>de sermo incidit, quia cum professis in 
          mi<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="31"/>nisteriis et in vitae genere conveniunt, 
          praeter<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="32"/>quam in modo votorum qua emittunt , et
          <lb ed="#C" n="33"/>consequenter in conditionibus quas 
          requi<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="34"/>runt ; quam differentiam hic explicare 
          ejus<lb break="no" ed="#C" n="35"/>que rationem reddere necesse est, simulque
          <lb ed="#C" n="36"/>quidquid his gradibus proprium ac speciale
          <lb ed="#C" n="37"/>fuerit declarabimus.
        </p>
      </div>
